This paper discusses the analysis of citations in scientific documents, which falls under the categories of digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), cybernetics (cs.CY), and social and information networks (cs.SI). The focus on technical developments and the use of computational and machine learning techniques also suggests a strong connection to these sub-categories.
